\b0 \cf0 \
This is release of cocoAspell package. This version supports Mac OS 10.5 and higher. If you are using any previous version of Mac OS X, you cannot use this software.\
\
This release supports both Mac OS X PowerPC and Mac OS X Intel. \
\
Old cocoAspell (cocoAspell 1.x) dictionaries are not compatible with this version. You will need to download and install new dictionaries. See "Installing a dictionary" section.\
